<header>
<div class="blogparent"><a href="../words" rel="tag">Words</a>:</div>
<h1>The Red Pill</h1>
<small>February 22, 2019</small>
</header>

<p>
To some, it’s just a blank page.<br>
To others, it’s their only stage.<br>
Whether you use it to channel your rage,<br>
Or simply want to make money with each turn of a page.
</p><p>
There’s an artist in you too, I swear.<br>
And no, this isn’t some stupid playground dare.<br>
I can see it in you, bursting at the seams, ready to freaking tear.<br>
But it’s not gonna be easy, and it’s not gonna feel very fair.
</p><p>
Now if that’s enough to stop you dead in your tracks,<br>
Then damn, hope you really enjoy wearing those navy slacks.
</p><p>
But if you think you might have a little fight left in you still,<br>
Then I’d encourage you to take a deep breath, and choose the <strong>red pill</strong>.
</p>


